                     <hi rend="largeCaps">ANN SMITH</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18470920-2040-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18470920-2040-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18470920-2040-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for unlawfully and knowingly uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
