                        <interp inst="t18470920-name-166" type="given" value="CALEB EDWARD"></interp>CALEB EDWARD POWELL.</persName>
                  </hi> I am solicitor to the Mint—this shilling is counterfeit—these other two are good, and both of George the Third's reign.</p>
